                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>Text I-2 includes the hymns:</note>
                     <note>- ʾO-ʾǝgzǝʾtǝyä Māryām walādita ʾamlāk ... "O my Lady Mary, Godbearing ..." (<locus target="#5va">5va-</locus>vb)</note>
                     <note>- ʾO-ʾǝgzǝʾtǝyä qǝddǝst dǝngǝl ba-kǝlʾe Māryām Mariham ʾǝmmu la-ʾIyasus Krǝstos kahāli ... "O my Lady, Holy Two-fold Virgin Mary, Mother of Jesus Christ the Almighty ..."(<locus target="#5vb">5vb</locus>) (cp. ChRep n<locus target="#373">373</locus>)</note>
                     <note>- ʾO-ʾǝgzǝʾtǝyä qǝddǝst Māryām ʾǝmma madḫǝn wa-ʾǝmma bǝrhān ... "O my Lady, Holy Virgin Mary, Mother of the Saviour and Mother of the Light ..." (<locus target="#6ra">6ra-</locus>vb).</note>
                     <note/>
                     <note>Text I-5 is distributed as follows: strophes 12-13 (<locus from="37ra" to="39rb">37ra-39rb</locus>); strophes 14-19 (<locus from="49ra" to="56vb">49ra-56vb</locus>); strophes 20-26 (<locus from="72va" to="83va">72va-83va</locus>); strophes 27-29 (<locus from="17ra" to="24va">17ra-24va</locus>); strophes 30-31, 33 (<locus from="11ra" to="14rb">11ra-14rb</locus>).</note>
                  </msItem>
